Mobile::Ads - Interface various Mobile Ads serving sites
======================================================================

DOCUMENTAION

For a detailed documentation see the man page:

   man Mobile::Ads

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   XML::LibXML
   LWP::UserAgent
   HTTP::Request::Common

